        <title>Measure Camshaft End Play</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Measure camshaft end play with a
                <hotlnk document="eges2101_X2100504.xml" xrefid="t210010504">Dial Indicator with Magnetic Base</hotlnk>
                . If the end play exceeds "
                <hotlnk document="eges2101_S210010507.xml" xrefid="t210010501">Specifications</hotlnk>
                ," camshaft has probably slipped back.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f210010521" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figeg5/EG5328.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"/>
            <caption>Measure camshaft end play</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove cam gear, pull camshaft forward. Repeat step 1.</para>
        </step1>
